I really really love how similar Jinx's one is to Yuno Gasai xD

EDIT: My phone hates me

If you type Yuno Gasai into Google Images, an image similar to Jinx's should be one of the first to appear. 

She is a pink-haired girl from an anime called Future Diary (or Mirai Nikki), and is one of the best yandere in anime. A yandere is a girl (or boy) who falls in love with someone, and then kills everyone who gets in their way, or even looks at her lover.
oh I know what mirai nikki and Yuno Gasai are, but what is yuni gasai
It's what happens when you try to write Japanese names on an Android phone with auto-correct.
